    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款有趣的异型拼图游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/extras/a66f969605683bc4d23de737ff4b5cc9.poster.avif?t=1741282114\" width=732 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/extras/a66f969605683bc4d23de737ff4b5cc9.webm?t=1741282114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/extras/a66f969605683bc4d23de737ff4b5cc9.mp4?t=1741282114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们还有有趣的猫猫！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/extras/c06c4c343a32806f01109ee78af16bb8.poster.avif?t=1741282114\" width=742 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/extras/c06c4c343a32806f01109ee78af16bb8.webm?t=1741282114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/extras/c06c4c343a32806f01109ee78af16bb8.mp4?t=1741282114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >养了一只'捣蛋鬼'后，我开发了一款治愈系解压游戏！🐱✨</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >说到开发这款游戏的灵感，就不得不提我家的小可爱皮皮了！一只集美貌与淘气于一身的小白猫！🤍</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/extras/df3ceb24803d7e97131366d73d070c4f.avif?t=1741282114\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/extras_big/df3ceb24803d7e97131366d73d070c4f.avif?t=1741282114 width=800 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/extras/860d99242815b7f1bdb5a00641f991ac.avif?t=1741282114\" width=800 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你们看这个小可爱！平时安静的时候可以萌化你的心～但是！！！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次看到它蹲在桌边磨爪子的时候，我的心都要跳出来了！😱</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/extras/e2828a1b3e6bfaf2f57d1f691da60ec6.avif?t=1741282114\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/extras_big/e2828a1b3e6bfaf2f57d1f691da60ec6.avif?t=1741282114 width=800 height=530 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就是这张无辜脸！！每次搞完破坏都是这个表情！气人又可爱！！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于日常被皮皮折磨（不是）的经历，我开发了这款《魔力拼图王2：反斗猫咪》🎮</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/extras/0397931112cb9e4e126a07823a301500.avif?t=1741282114\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/extras_big/0397931112cb9e4e126a07823a301500.avif?t=1741282114 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏设定超有趣：<br>✨ 主角是一只捣蛋猫咪（当然是以皮皮为原型啦！）<br>✨ 关卡设计全部来自猫咪和他的好友们<br>✨ 每个关卡都是被猫主子打碎的物品<br>✨ 玩家需要通过拼图把物品复原</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特色：<br>🎯 难度递进，从简单到困难共15关<br>🎵 超治愈的音乐，边玩边解压<br>🌈 清新文艺的画风，猫咪超可爱<br>🎮 操作简单，老少皆宜</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重点安利：<br>💝 整个拼图过程中都有可爱的猫咪随时出现打扰你哦。<br>💝 本作本体完全免费，免费游玩本体15关。<br>💝 超多DLC提供猫咪和他的有趣可爱的盆友们，以及额外的关卡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从一个被猫主子折磨的铲屎官，到一个游戏开发者，这大概就是我的养猫副产品吧～🥰</p>",
